  "text": [
    "Hair rush, low swoop\u2014",
    "so those of us",
    "stuck here on earth",
    "know\u2014you must be gods.",
    "Or friends of gods,",
    "granted chances",
    "to push off into sky,",
    "granted chances",
    "to hear so well",
    "your own voice bounced",
    "back to you",
    "maps the night.",
    "Each hinge",
    "in your wing\u2019s",
    "an act of creation.",
    "Each insect",
    "you snick out of air",
    "a witness.",
    "You transform",
    "obstacles",
    "into sounds,",
    "then dodge them."
  ],
  "title": "Spirit of the Bat",
  "year": ""
}